text: Rainbow Butterfly Unicorn Kitty (shorter name RBUK) is a American animated series. Its first episode was seen on Nickelodeon on January 27, 2019. It previously aired reruns on Nicktoons until December 20, 2019. == Episodes == ===Season 1 (2019)=== Episode Name First aired Episode number in season Purrfect Party January 27, 2019 1A Anubis Newbie January 27, 2019 1B == Notes == == References == Category:2019 American television series debuts Category:2019 Canadian television series endings Category:Nickelodeon television series Category:English-language television programs
